snippet.title: President Biden Farts In Front of Royalty: Week In Review | The Amber Ruffin Show
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

During the recent U.N. Climate Summit in Scotland, President Biden reportedly let out a “long, loud fart” in front of Britain’s Duchess Camilla Parker Bowles. That is a real thing that happened. Plus, Amazon goes maskless, People announces 2021’s “Sexiest Man Alive,” and Congress passes a $1 trillion infrastructure bill (but it isn't nearly enough). 

 #TheAmberRuffinShow #PeacockTV #Biden

Show Synopsis: Amber showcases her signature smart-and-silly take on the news of the week, responding to it all with a charming, late-night mix of seriousness, nonsense, and evening gowns.
